<taxonomicName authorityName="Buenaventura &amp; Pape" authorityYear="2013" box="[460,774,1338,1363]" class="Insecta" family="Sarcophagidae" genus="Peckia" kingdom="Fungi" order="Diptera" pageId="64" pageNumber="65" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="sarmientoi" subGenus="Peckia">
<emphasis box="[460,536,1339,1363]" italics="true" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">Peckia</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[557,633,1339,1363]" italics="true" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">Peckia</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[654,774,1339,1362]" italics="true" pageId="64" pageNumber="65">sarmientoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has the juxtal lateral plate with outer margin spinose, a feature only found in this species.
</paragraph>
